item.title: CVE-2022-24923|2024-08-03T04:29:00.709Z -- samsung%20mobile -- searchwidget
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in Samsung SearchWidget prior to versions 2.3.00.6 in China models allows untrusted applications to load arbitrary URL and local files in webview.
